column5: great art work....but I just don't understand this tattoo craze it is just not for me but then again I am older ,plus I can think of many other things to spend my money on. Although at one time back in the 80s I was that close to getting the Rolling Stones logo on my left chest but chickened out in the waiting room at the shop. It was only going to be 40 bucks.
